{"tid":1885483,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU方面公開惡意留言起訴進展 正在以此進行處罰","createTime":"2020-02-18T10:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T10:51:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c2d585653c697d7f4b2fa385d27316d3ec60c7","tid":1885483,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"bnt新聞訊 韓國人氣歌手兼演員IU方面公開了對惡意留言的起訴進展情況。<br />\n<br />\n17日，IU所屬社EDAM娛樂通過官方推特表示：「如2019年10月18日公告所示，對IU進行惡意誹謗的帖子已經收到了起訴狀。 大多數嫌疑人的身份都得到了確認，並接受了調查機關的調查。 」並解釋道：「雖然很難根據調查機關的要求公開具體的過程和詳細的進展情況，但是正在依次進行處罰，等待結果通知」，「今後通過不斷監測和粉絲舉報，將持續進行強硬法律應對」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，IU方面去年10月曾公告稱：「我們認為盲目的惡意留言和散佈虛假事實造成的名譽毀損、性騷擾、人身攻擊等程度非常嚴重，因此將對此採取法律措施」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://n.yam.com/Article/20200218940724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.yam.com%2FArticle%2F20200218940724&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmj11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=89eb2210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://n.yam.com/Article/20200218940724</a>"},{"pid":"6098634232cc20dd19f5dfd324163648aad966f4","tid":1885483,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"今次大穫了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775bf987c312844e4765c7eb4fd894352c40b329","tid":1885483,"uid":325869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"言論自由....<br />\n<br />\n新加坡都冇了，然後到南韓"},{"pid":"6a179937e964179f5c376044f634b6fbf462b6c8","tid":1885483,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"#李知恩圖報"},{"pid":"65d977576a60b8f522a9dc02f504a36f911365a8","tid":1885483,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6de8ed7a51e491472d209439c654405b/a6a2aeef2f8b5fdb-cd/s540x810/78fec3a8e7b477706f96e81b5a5401af9f41ce91.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.